data.description: Affordable home in a fantastic Prairieville location!  Grab your agent and schedule your tour ASAP.  Three bedrooms two baths with granite countertops, beautiful laminate flooring throughout, custom kitchen cabinets, large family room, master bath with double vanities and a shower.  Enjoy the peace of mind you get from your fully fenced back yard with a six foot wood privacy fence with a large gate at the front.  Plenty of parking space for your family and friends with your double wide driveway and large single car car port.  Beautiful painted brick and vinyl siding exterior is maintenance free.  Roof is 30 year architectural shingles.  Come take a look now.
